OL,3,CNissan to cut 9,000 jobs globally as
OL,4,Coperating profit forecast slashed by
OL,5,C70%
OL,7,FNissan has stated that it will be
OL,8,Fcutting 9,000 jobs globally while
OL,9,Fthrottling back production by 20 per
OL,10,Fcent amid sweeping cost-saving
OL,11,Fmeasures.
OL,13,FThe Japanese firm cut its operating
OL,14,Fprofit forecast this morning by 70 per
OL,15,Fcent to 150bn yen, or around #754m. It
OL,16,Falso plans to sell up to 10 per cent
OL,17,Fof Mitsubishi Motors as a way of
OL,18,Fboosting funds. In the first half of
OL,19,Fthe year, global sales fell 3.8% and
OL,20,Foperating profit in Q2 was down 85%.
