OL,7,FIn its report for the first-half
OL,8,Fresults for the fiscal year, Nissan
OL,9,FCEO Makoto Uchida said the move did
OL,10,Fnot signal a "shrinking" of the
OL,11,Fcompany.
OL,13,FHe said: "These turnaround measures do
OL,14,Fnot imply that the company is
OL,15,Fshrinking. Nissan will restructure its
OL,16,Fbusiness to become leaner and more
OL,17,Fresilient, while also reorganizing
OL,18,Fmanagement to respond quickly and
OL,19,Fflexibly to changes in the business
OL,20,Fenvironment.
