OL,5,C70%
OL,7,F"We aim to enhance the competitiveness
OL,8,Fof our products, which are fundamental
OL,9,Fto our success and set Nissan back on
OL,10,Fa path of growth.
OL,12,F"As a cohesive team, we are dedicated
OL,13,Fto working together to ensure the
OL,14,Fsuccessful implementation of our
OL,15,Fplans."
OL,17,FThe announced cuts cover seven per
OL,18,Fcent of the brand's global employees,
OL,19,Fwhich currently stands at more than
OL,20,F133,000 people worldwide.
