OL,7,FNissan has yet to announce what these
OL,8,Fchanges could mean for its UK-based
OL,9,Foperations, but a spokesperson for the
OL,10,Fmain union, Unite, told ITV Tyne Tees
OL,11,Fit is understood that job-losses will
OL,12,Fnot affect Sunderland.
OL,14,FIts production site on Wearside
OL,15,Fcurrently builds a number of its core
OL,16,Fmodels including the Qashqai and Juke,
OL,17,Fand as of June last year, has a
OL,18,Fworkforce of around 6,000 people.
