OL,7,FNissan recently confirmed that it
OL,8,Fwould be building electric versions of
OL,9,Fthe Qashqai, Juke and Leaf at
OL,10,FSunderland amid its electrification
OL,11,Fplans.
OL,13,FThe Nissan president said he would
OL,14,Falso voluntarily forfeit 50% of his
OL,15,Fmonthly compensation starting in
OL,16,FNovember 2024 while other executive
OL,17,Fcommittee members will voluntarily
OL,18,Ftake a pay reduction accordingly.
